GI problems in children: I.

INTESTINAL-DISEASES: di, th.

CELIAC-DISEASE: di, th.  CHILD.  CHILD-PRESCHOOL.
COLITIS-ULCERATIVE: di, th.  CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: di, th.
DISACCHARIDASES: df.  CROHN-DISEASE: di, th.  HUMAN.  INFANT.
INFANT-NEWBORN.  INFANT-PREMATURE.
LYMPHANGIECTASIS-INTESTINAL: di, th.

The first of two articles focuses on a number of malabsorptive
disorders and on inflammatory bowel diseases as causes of persistent
diarrhea.  Diagnosis and treatment of the different entities are
detailed.

